data.eml:eml: A new species of Cyrtodactylus Gray, 1826 (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Khanh Hoa province, Southern Vietnam

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Tri, Ngo Van, Onn, Chan Kin (2010): A new species of Cyrtodactylus Gray, 1826 (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Khanh Hoa province, Southern Vietnam. Zootaxa 2504: 47-60, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.293249
